{
  "stem": "10406.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But most people did not want to be involved in that because if something happened and the judenrat rather tried to represent the Jews, and let's say protested, so they took them and shot them and they-- they said, form another one.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but now, the judenrat would order-- let's say the Germans wanted 50 people, 100 people to do work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would have to provide them, and that was on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, they would also-- the Germans would also go, suddenly appear in town, and-- and whoever was Jewish-- and, of course, the Jews had to wear bands.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you remember getting a band?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have to wear it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother and sister already wore it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it's interesting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have running water in our house, but there was a pump about a block away, so we had to go to get water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we already knew the fear was there that you can be captured any time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So being that they were wearing-- we had two kinds of situations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The white bands were the star of David, and they also made us wear yellow circles in the front and in the back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, every Jewish home had to be-- had to be marked with a yellow circle or maybe larger, maybe 8 inches in diameter, so they in a way knew which were the Jewish homes, and they knew if you walked on the streets, they knew who was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they would just grab people and then take them to do work, and it could be-- it could be sweeping the streets, or it could be to the headquarters to do work, or whatever, you know?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then at the end of the day towards late afternoon, they would let them go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What were you starting to say about with going for the water?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were in the middle of a thought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So being that-- that's one of my habits.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I jump to other things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have a lot of things-- Yeah, other people tell me the same thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I would volunteer to go to get the water because I didn't wear the--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was too-- I was too young to wear it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they started with 12.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was 10 at that point, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't have to-- I didn't have to wear it, so I used to volunteer to go to get the water.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was heavy, you know, with the pails.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to carry it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then I learned that if you balance out with two pails, it's much easier than with one pail that unbalances you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was-- it was a--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a tense situation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not as much as my brother would be afraid or my sister because they were already older, that they could be grabbed for labor or for whatever, you know?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or to be killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the atmosphere was tense.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the stores were already closed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in other words, the stores were closed up during the Russian occupation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So basically, most Jews had nothing to it was difficult to make a living already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you had to buy and sell, and sort of black market if you had some things to sell.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Farmers would still come into town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, we had this particular farm family named [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[POLISH] means 'plum' in Polish, so it was an easy name to remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And maybe that name saved my life later on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This particular family would come to our house, and they would bring butter and cheese and eggs and my mother would give them-- give them some materials to make a dress or a suit.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was a bartering type of situation that sort of helped us get food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And most people had that-- had a problem with it, and that was one way of doing it somehow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or doing some work still and maybe making some money, not directly because Jews were not allowed to have businesses or to do anything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then the winter approached.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember-- I remember once there was a snowstorm, and there was a lot of snow piled up on the sides.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in our town, when the snow came, you don't-- well, we didn't have cars per se, you know, so it was either wagons on wheels, and then during the winter, there were sleds.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, horse-pulled sleds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I saw one of my teachers-- religious, Hebrew teacher, who must have been in the 70s, who was walking.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the older people wore, like, the hats were, like, Hasidic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, even though they were Hasidic, they were actually Russian czarist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were round with one of these things in the front.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
